title: AIRZONE - World's First Indoor Atrium Net Playground
blurb: Bouncy nets spanning levels 2 to 6 of the mall atrium.
description: AIRZONE is the world's first indoor atrium net playground. It features bouncy nets that span levels 2 to 6 of the mall atrium, slides to connect one level to the next, and various activities to enjoy. Visitors can explore different zones within the net structure, offering a unique and thrilling experience for families and children. It's a great place for kids and adults to have fun and be active in a safe and engaging environment. The playground provides a memorable adventure for all ages.
age_group_display: Suitable for all ages (Children below 5 years old must be accompanied by a supervising adult with separate ticket)
